Tell HN: I have an idea of a smartphone application
text:
Please help me to develop my favorite idea. This is a calendar for the Nature. I did not think about the source of information but I want to open the app and to observe what regular events are coming right now. Examples of such events: some plant is flowering, one of regular comet rains, some birds are returning from the South, the shortest or longest day and after enough research it will be dozens of that events per day.

Please help me to define a stack of technologies and minimal possible budget assuming I have the data and knowledge of few programming languages but do not have any database and hosting biases.
